|Entailments={{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=(obligation of) paying taxes negatively affects the taxpayer
|Entailment.Source inference=presence of burden negatively affects burdened_entity's ability to move or act
}}{{Entailment
|Entailment.Target entailment=amount of taxes is related to degree to which taxpayer is affected
|Entailment.Source inference=weight of burden is related to degree of (negative) effect; heavy burdens have more effect than lighter ones
|Entailment.Type=scalar
}}
